Package: snakemakeR
Title: Consstruct snakemake rules from R scripts
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Amel", "Zulji", , "zuljiamel1991@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Helpers for building snakemake rules and inserting them in the current snakemake workflow. Each R script starts with a mock S4 snakemake object from which the package pull all necessary infrmation for building and inserting the rules the rules.
